Opinion TRAGIC END ‘Badly decomposed’ body of missing mum Karen Ristevski, 47, found wedged inside a fallen tree eight months after she vanished amid fears she was murdered 
The positive id follows forensic tests carried out on the body found in bush 30 miles from the site where she was last seen by jon lockett
